'''Wilcome Cotton''' refers to two members of the [[Cotton Family]]:

* [[Wilcome Cotton I|Wilcome ("Will") Cotton]] (born {{SR|1346}}), son of [[Holman Cotton|Holman ("Long Holm") Cotton]] and uncle of [[Rose Cotton]].
* [[Wilcome Cotton II|Wilcome ("Jolly") Cotton]] (born {{SR|1384}}), son of [[Tolman Cotton Senior|Tolman ("Tom") Cotton Senior]] and brother of [[Rose Cotton]].
